# ENTITY::SET_CAN_CLIMB_ON_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity
* **BOOL** canClimb

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Prevent climbing on a particular entity.

p1 always false.
